headline: Does Booking Present an Opportunity After Ryanair Legal Dispute Resolution?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Booking Holdings stock? You are not alone. Investors are weighing up the recent dips and surges, trying to figure out whether this online travel heavyweight still has room to run, or if the best days are already in the rearview mirror. After touching impressive highs, Booking’s share price has cooled off a bit lately, dropping 3.1% over the last week and 3.7% in the past month.
